headline: WPS named best midsize utility in the Midwest at keeping the lights on for customers
summary: Wisconsin Public Service (WPS) is once again earning national recognition for its commitment to world-class reliability and customer service. The company has been named one of the top performing midsize utilities as part of PA Consulting's 2024 ReliabilityOne® Awards.
